### Test Attendance Corrections API
### Replace {{token}} with actual JWT token from HR login

### 1. Get all corrections (HR/ADMIN only)
GET http://localhost:3333/attendance-corrections
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get pending corrections (HR/ADMIN only)
GET http://localhost:3333/attendance-corrections/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get my corrections (Employee)
GET http://localhost:3333/attendance-corrections/my-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get corrections with status filter
GET http://localhost:3333/attendance-corrections?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get corrections by employee
GET http://localhost:3333/attendance-corrections?employeeId=EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
